column16: Kosuke Fukudome grounds into double play, pitcher Kevin Mulvey to shortstop Stephen Drew to first baseman Mark Reynolds.    Ryan Theriot out at 2nd.
Ryan Theriot singles on a ground ball to center fielder Chris Young.    Xavier Nady to 2nd.
Geovany Soto flies out to right fielder Justin Upton.
Mike Fontenot grounds out to first baseman Mark Reynolds.
Alfonso Soriano lines out to third baseman Augie Ojeda.
Chad Tracy singles on a ground ball to shortstop Stephen Drew, deflected by third baseman Augie Ojeda.    Derrek Lee to 3rd.    Marlon Byrd to 2nd.
Marlon Byrd singles on a soft line drive to right fielder Justin Upton.    Derrek Lee to 2nd.
Kosuke Fukudome flies out to left fielder Rusty Ryal.
Tyler Colvin lines out to third baseman Mark Reynolds in foul territory.
Derrek Lee reaches on force attempt, missed catch error by shortstop Stephen Drew, assist to second baseman Kelly Johnson.    Kosuke Fukudome to 2nd.
Ryan Theriot flies out to right fielder Justin Upton.
Marlon Byrd homers (4) on a fly ball to left field.
Geovany Soto homers (3) on a fly ball to left field.
